    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh okay, wait. you mentioned antibiotic ointment? i saw some stuff at the convenience store that has a little bit of antibiotic in it for cuts, could i just put a tiny bit of that on my eye if the drops don't work? i just need to get through this work week without losing vision or anything lol",
